title: clone
description: Clones a set of blocks from one region to another.

fields.title: begin
fields.description: A `vector` that specifies the location in `x`, `y`, and `z` coordinates of `float` type.

fields.title: end
fields.description: A `vector` that specifies the location in `x`, `y`, and `z` coordinates of `float` type.

fields.title: destination
fields.description: A `vector` that specifies the location in `x`, `y`, and `z` coordinates of `float` type. The lower northwest corner of the region being cloned.

fields.title: maskMode
fields.description: An `enum` that filters the blocks being cloned. If type `masked`, copy non-air blocks.

fields.title: cloneMode
fields.description: An `enum` that is one of type `force`, `move`, or `normal`. Default: `normal`.

fields.title: tileName
fields.description: An `enum` that must be the `block name` of the blocks that are to be cloned.

fields.title: blockStates
fields.description: An `array` of block states. Specifies the block  states to use for the cloned blocks.

overloads.title: Clone with optional `maskMode`, `cloneMode`
overloads.description: Clone a set of blocks from one location to a destination with an optional `maskMode` and `cloneMode`.

overloads.title: Clone with optional `maskMode`, `cloneMode`, `tileName`, `blockStates`
overloads.description: Clone a set of blocks from one location to a destination with an optional `maskMode` and `cloneMode`, as well as optional `tileName` or `blockStates` data  to specify the blocks to clone.
